{"tid":1813109,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"(襲警rip)  綠van大埔撼「訓練」警車 6人傷送院","createTime":"2020-01-06T04:39:18.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-06T04:41:50.000Z","uid":184679,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"7d95cd9e5e3fa21326ff5850e0bda59f3e0673b9","tid":1813109,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-06T04:39:18.000Z","msg":"一輛502號線往大埔那打素醫院的載客專線小巴，早上9時40分，駛至大埔公路大窩段近水圍時，撞倒前面一輛警車，意外中，6名男女受傷，包括小巴男司機及5名小巴乘客，而警車上的警長及警員均無受傷。警方到場，傷者送院治理，警方正調查意外原因，小巴事後由拖車拖走。<br />\n<br />\n意外後，小巴擋風玻璃爆裂，左車頭損毀，警車車尾右邊擋風玻璃亦碎掉。<br />\n<br />\n據悉，涉事警車車頭車尾均掛有「訓練司機」牌，意外前，小巴及警車雙雙駛近水圍期間，警車疑快到燈位，司機收慢車速，小巴司機收掣不及，撞向警車車尾。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E7%B6%A0van%E5%A4%A7%E5%9F%94%E6%92%BC-%E8%A8%93%E7%B7%B4-%E8%AD%A6%E8%BB%8A-6%E4%BA%BA%E5%82%B7%E9%80%81%E9%99%A2-032200726.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.yahoo.com%2F%25E7%25B6%25A0van%25E5%25A4%25A7%25E5%259F%2594%25E6%2592%25BC-%25E8%25A8%2593%25E7%25B7%25B4-%25E8%25AD%25A6%25E8%25BB%258A-6%25E4%25BA%25BA%25E5%2582%25B7%25E9%2580%2581%25E9%2599%25A2-032200726.html&d=bwUHcV0Pscj1NrVo4Cy%2FDaS5T01Y9%2BWuDWMC0%2BQyx7Y%3D&h=c1036efc\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E7%B6%A0van%E5%A4%A7%E5%9F%94%E6%92%BC-%E8%A8%93%E7%B7%B4-%E8%AD%A6%E8%BB%8A-6%E4%BA%BA%E5%82%B7%E9%80%81%E9%99%A2-032200726.html</a>"},{"pid":"f0a487507736fa7544a9612a8cfa4f76e888d1f1","tid":1813109,"uid":8014,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-06T04:40:43.000Z","msg":"架車多過3個人，應該告暴動<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n義士<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"04fccf32aa7af2db74dc0bba74cc47e081cd68c6","tid":1813109,"uid":222970,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-06T04:41:07.000Z","msg":"司機係手足<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b144f9d601c5599b4719a5a5c6c46ff2e0b3a6e6","tid":1813109,"uid":15812,"